{
  "number": 77,
  "name": "Al-Mursalaat",
  "arabicName": "سُورَةُ المُرۡسَلَاتِ",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "totalAyahs": 50,
  "translator": "Saheeh International",
  "edition": "en.sahih",
  "language": "English",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "By those [winds] sent forth in gusts",
      "ayah_number": 1,
      "verse_key": "77:1"
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "And the winds that blow violently",
      "ayah_number": 2,
      "verse_key": "77:2"
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "And [by] the winds that spread [clouds]",
      "ayah_number": 3,
      "verse_key": "77:3"
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "And those [angels] who bring criterion",
      "ayah_number": 4,
      "verse_key": "77:4"
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "And those [angels] who deliver a message",
      "ayah_number": 5,
      "verse_key": "77:5"
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "As justification or warning,",
      "ayah_number": 6,
      "verse_key": "77:6"
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Indeed, what you are promised is to occur.",
      "ayah_number": 7,
      "verse_key": "77:7"
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "So when the stars are obliterated",
      "ayah_number": 8,
      "verse_key": "77:8"
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "And when the heaven is opened",
      "ayah_number": 9,
      "verse_key": "77:9"
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "And when the mountains are blown away",
      "ayah_number": 10,
      "verse_key": "77:10"
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "And when the messengers' time has come...",
      "ayah_number": 11,
      "verse_key": "77:11"
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "For what Day was it postponed?",
      "ayah_number": 12,
      "verse_key": "77:12"
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "For the Day of Judgement.",
      "ayah_number": 13,
      "verse_key": "77:13"
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "And what can make you know what is the Day of Judgement?",
      "ayah_number": 14,
      "verse_key": "77:14"
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 15,
      "verse_key": "77:15"
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Did We not destroy the former peoples?",
      "ayah_number": 16,
      "verse_key": "77:16"
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "Then We will follow them with the later ones.",
      "ayah_number": 17,
      "verse_key": "77:17"
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "Thus do We deal with the criminals.",
      "ayah_number": 18,
      "verse_key": "77:18"
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 19,
      "verse_key": "77:19"
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "Did We not create you from a liquid disdained?",
      "ayah_number": 20,
      "verse_key": "77:20"
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "And We placed it in a firm lodging",
      "ayah_number": 21,
      "verse_key": "77:21"
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "For a known extent.",
      "ayah_number": 22,
      "verse_key": "77:22"
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "And We determined [it], and excellent [are We] to determine.",
      "ayah_number": 23,
      "verse_key": "77:23"
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 24,
      "verse_key": "77:24"
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "Have We not made the earth a container",
      "ayah_number": 25,
      "verse_key": "77:25"
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "Of the living and the dead?",
      "ayah_number": 26,
      "verse_key": "77:26"
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And We placed therein lofty, firmly set mountains and have given you to drink sweet water.",
      "ayah_number": 27,
      "verse_key": "77:27"
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 28,
      "verse_key": "77:28"
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "[They will be told], \"Proceed to that which you used to deny.",
      "ayah_number": 29,
      "verse_key": "77:29"
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "Proceed to a shadow [of smoke] having three columns",
      "ayah_number": 30,
      "verse_key": "77:30"
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "[But having] no cool shade and availing not against the flame.\"",
      "ayah_number": 31,
      "verse_key": "77:31"
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "Indeed, it throws sparks [as huge] as a fortress,",
      "ayah_number": 32,
      "verse_key": "77:32"
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "As if they were yellowish [black] camels.",
      "ayah_number": 33,
      "verse_key": "77:33"
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 34,
      "verse_key": "77:34"
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "This is a Day they will not speak,",
      "ayah_number": 35,
      "verse_key": "77:35"
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "Nor will it be permitted for them to make an excuse.",
      "ayah_number": 36,
      "verse_key": "77:36"
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 37,
      "verse_key": "77:37"
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "This is the Day of Judgement; We will have assembled you and the former peoples.",
      "ayah_number": 38,
      "verse_key": "77:38"
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "So if you have a plan, then plan against Me.",
      "ayah_number": 39,
      "verse_key": "77:39"
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 40,
      "verse_key": "77:40"
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "Indeed, the righteous will be among shades and springs",
      "ayah_number": 41,
      "verse_key": "77:41"
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "And fruits from whatever they desire,",
      "ayah_number": 42,
      "verse_key": "77:42"
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "[Being told], \"Eat and drink in satisfaction for what you used to do.\"",
      "ayah_number": 43,
      "verse_key": "77:43"
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "Indeed, We thus reward the doers of good.",
      "ayah_number": 44,
      "verse_key": "77:44"
    },
    {
      "number": 45,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 45,
      "verse_key": "77:45"
    },
    {
      "number": 46,
      "text": "[O disbelievers], eat and enjoy yourselves a little; indeed, you are criminals.",
      "ayah_number": 46,
      "verse_key": "77:46"
    },
    {
      "number": 47,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 47,
      "verse_key": "77:47"
    },
    {
      "number": 48,
      "text": "And when it is said to them, \"Bow [in prayer],\" they do not bow.",
      "ayah_number": 48,
      "verse_key": "77:48"
    },
    {
      "number": 49,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
      "ayah_number": 49,
      "verse_key": "77:49"
    },
    {
      "number": 50,
      "text": "Then in what statement after the Qur'an will they believe?",
      "ayah_number": 50,
      "verse_key": "77:50"
    }
  ]
}